org.hypknowsys.wumprep.configeditor
Interface ContextHelpChangeListener

All Known Implementing Classes:
WUMprepConfigEditor
public interface ContextHelpChangeListener

Interface to be implemented by classes that should be notified about a change of the context help text describing the currently selected item of a WUMprepConfigEditor.
